<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Anthem" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Anthem,</orth> a song performed as part of divine service: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.213" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 213</bibl>; and then in general a solemn and mournful song: <bibl n="shak. ven 839" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 839</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. pht 21" default="NO" valid="yes">Phoen. 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.240" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. III, 1, 240</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>